ELF3D - OpenSource Lightweight 3D Game Engine
=============================================

ELF3D is an Open Source Game Engine that has a main goal of being an all in Game Engine. ELF3D is not only is a Graphics, Window, Input, Physics, Sound, or Network Manager, it is all of those managers combined into one simple, free, opensource, and lightweight Game Engine.

ELF3D is written in C++ and uses OpenGL for 3D Graphics.

